These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Transport: ship, roller, skateboard, train
Pet: horse, rat, pony, bird
1. Pet:rat is on the left of Pet:horse##1
2. Transport:ship == Pet:bird##1
3. Pet:pony is on the right of Pet:horse##1
4. Transport:roller is on the left of Pet:bird##1
5. Transport:train is on the left of Pet:horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Transport          | train | skateboard | roller | ship   |
| Pet   | rat  | horse     | pony   | bird |

