.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Job: dressmaker, doctor, journalist, firefighter
Cigar: pall-mall, swisher, havana, ritmeester
1. Job:firefighter == Cigar:swisher##1
2. Job:dressmaker is on the far right##1
3. Job:doctor is on the right of Job:firefighter##1
4. Job:firefighter is on the right of Cigar:havana##1
5. Cigar:swisher is on the left of Cigar:pall-mall##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | journalist | firefighter | doctor | dressmaker    |
| Cigar   | havana    | swisher      | pall-mall | ritmeester |

