.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
City: venice, marseilles, london, new-york
Cigar: montecristo, tiparillo, fonseca, bluemaster
1. Cigar:montecristo is on the left of City:marseilles##1
2. Cigar:tiparillo is on the left of City:new-york##1
3. City:venice is on the left of City:london##1
4. City:new-york == Cigar:bluemaster##1
5. Cigar:montecristo is on the left of City:marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City   | venice | london | marseilles | new-york   |
| Cigar     | fonseca  | montecristo    | tiparillo       | bluemaster |

 